# Backend Architecture Design: Collaborative AI Code Editor

> [!NOTE]
> This document outlines the complete, production-grade backend architecture for the Online Collaborative AI Code Editor. It serves as the foundational blueprint for all subsequent development, ensuring modularity, scalability, and maintainability.

